  "description": "Torus T(7,3) at near-maximum feedback (0.92) and tangle (0.85) — the spiral wraps 7 times in one direction and 3 in the other, creating complex harmonic interference that spirals outward. At 4.0 Hz pulse, the spiral accelerates. This is the sound of resonance trying to reach infinity.",
